@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uftztp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.sin((v2 + 0.06 * tmp + 0.37)))
    v2 = ((0.20 - wp.abs(tmp + 0.30)) + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.33) * (v2 + 0.15 - tmp + 0.39)))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.93) - (v0 + 0.17 - v1 + 0.57)) + wp.cos((v0 + 0.63 / v2 + 0.58)))
    v0 = 0.50
    v0 = v0
    v0 = 0.24
    data[tid] = v0
